description: Represents affection or love between two women, with one having a medium-light skin tone. This emoji signifies romantic relationships and deep emotional bonds.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this kiss emoji depicts two women, one with no specific skin tone and another with a medium-light skin tone, sharing a loving moment. Their faces are rendered with Apple's characteristic soft, rounded edges and gentle shading, emphasizing tenderness and affection. The subtle highlight on their lips conveys the intimacy of the kiss, making it a sweet and inclusive representation of romantic love as designed by Apple.
